  <div class="page">
    <header>
      <span class="pill">Portfolio Case Study</span>
      <h1>Bellabeat Capstone: Fitbit Data Analysis</h1>
      <div class="subtitle">by <strong>Ben Halperin</strong> · Data / Business Analytics</div>
      <p class="tagline">
        An end-to-end analysis of Fitbit activity and sleep data to generate actionable marketing
        insights for Bellabeat’s women-focused wellness products.
      </p>
    </header>

    <section>
      <h2>Project Overview</h2>
      <p>
        This capstone follows the Google Data Analytics "Ask, Prepare, Process, Analyze, Share, Act"
        framework. Using real Fitbit tracker data, I explored how user activity, sleep, and engagement
        patterns can inform Bellabeat’s marketing and product strategy.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Tools: R, RStudio, tidyverse, janitor, lubridate, R Markdown</li>
        <li>Data: Fitbit Fitness Tracker Data (Kaggle, CC0, 30 users, 2016)</li>
        <li>Focus: activity patterns, sleep behavior, user segments, engagement opportunities</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Deliverables</h2>
